          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/315_step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, drain and run the <strong>potatoes</strong> under <strong>cold water</strong> until cool enough to handle</p><p>Mash them until smooth</p><p>Add half of the <strong>chopped chives</strong>, 2-3 tbsp <strong>olive oil</strong> and season generously with both<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, then mix to combine</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/315_step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
