    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 5 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[10 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and mix to combine into a dough</p><p>Place the <strong>dough</strong> onto a floured surface and bring it together into a ball with your hands</p><p>Divide the ball into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> pieces and roll each into a golf ball shape</p><p>Pat each ball down and sprinkle with a little<strong> flour </strong>– these are your <strong>potato cakes</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
